2026-06-30T02:10:55+00:00	openclaw.audit	{"payload":{"type":"TOOL_POLICY_EVALUATION","spiffeId":"spiffe://example.org/ns/apps/sa/gateway-1","agentId":"8ea675ca-1539-46f2-9ca0-57c278888fe4","toolName":"write","params":{"path":"testing2.md","content":"# Testing, Take Two\n\nThe first one passed, the second failed,\nThe third one quietly derailed.\nGreen checkmarks line up, row on row,\nThen one turns red and steals the show.\n\nA flaky test, a phantom thread,\nA race condition best left dead—\nIt works on mine, it breaks on yours,\nThe oldest of debugging lores.\n\nMock the world and stub the call,\nPretend you've reasoned through it all.\nBut truth lives only in the run,\nAnd not in proofs you think you've done.\n\nSo here's to red that turns to green,\nThe cleanest sight you've ever seen—\nNot faith, not hope, not clever guess,\nBut evidence of correctness.\n"},"timestamp":1782785455254},"signature":"MEQCIBo3b6WBqIUrPqNmJwuFG8+tQ8EKFk7PU5gwFZU2pRHZAiAvC8CZ4gPPqsQJDwzfu1Lw0aRqv+w5WNNQiQBek8kgYA=="}
